# ml_models/
#
# Trained model artifacts are written here by the ml_retrain DAG (Sundays 03:00 UTC).
# Files committed to git: this .gitkeep only.
# Actual artifacts (.joblib) are excluded via .gitignore.
#
# Expected contents after first retrain:
#   forecaster_{route_id}_{cabin}.joblib   — AutoARIMA
#   anomaly_{route_id}_{cabin}.joblib      — IsolationForest
#   expected_price_global.joblib           — LightGBM regressor
